Do you think I'm lying to you?

291
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,660
The municipal PSB has directed

292
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:56,660
Limin to be specifically responsible

293
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:58,100
for your and Songge's safety.

294
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:59,020
Starting tomorrow,

295
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:01,420
neither of you can go wandering around.

296
00:19:02,300 --> 00:19:03,140
Got it.

297
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:04,700
By the way, Dad,

298
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,340
how is Mr. Huang doing?

299
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:09,180
He's okay.

300
00:19:09,180 --> 00:19:10,810
He can be discharged
in a couple of days.

301
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,700
That's good.

302
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:13,700
Dad,

303
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:15,820
I was thinking,

304
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,140
could it have been

305
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:20,900
Huo Kaiming who smashed my car?

306
00:19:21,770 --> 00:19:23,780
Why are you two taking
so long to wash your hands?

307
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:24,860
Hurry up and eat.

308
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:25,940
Coming!

309
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:27,780
Don't tell your mom.

310
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:34,220
Coming.

311
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:36,420
What a feast!

312
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:37,260
Sit over there.

313
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:38,260
Hui,

314
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:39,460
- you sit here.
- Okay.

315
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:40,660
This is quite a feast.

316
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:47,500
Delicious.

317
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:48,420
It's good.

318
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:14,450
What's wrong, Mom?

319
00:20:15,780 --> 00:20:16,620
Nothing.

320
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:18,780
Watching you

321
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:19,940
eat with your dad

322
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:22,660
makes me feel really happy.

323
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:28,140
Why are you crying if you're happy?

324
00:20:28,980 --> 00:20:29,820
I'm not crying.

325
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:35,700
Hui,

326
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:37,100
try to come home

327
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,700
for dinner more often.

328
00:20:38,700 --> 00:20:40,100
Your dad actually

329
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:41,260
misses you a lot.

330
00:20:44,940 --> 00:20:45,780
I never said that.

331
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:47,980
You didn't say it,

332
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:49,740
but that's what you're thinking.

333
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:52,180
Don't you miss him even more?

334
00:20:52,180 --> 00:20:54,310
You missed him so much you cried,
yet you won't admit it.

335
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:02,140
Mom,

336
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:03,340
don't worry.

337
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,220
I'll come back often.

338
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:08,660
Eat up.

339
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,180
Let's eat.

340
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:27,400
Let me get you some more.

341
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:29,500
Eat more meat.

342
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:30,940
You have some too.

343
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:32,500
I'll get it myself.

344
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,340
I'll get it for you.

345
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:34,740
Fine.

346
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:51,060
It's this one, right?

347
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:52,000
Yes, this is the room.

348
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,460
Songge.

349
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:56,300
I'm Limin.

350
00:21:57,620 --> 00:21:58,460
Songge!

351
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:01,500
Is no one here?

352
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,980
I don't know, I just started my shift.

353
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:03,980
Open the door, quick.

354
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:06,620
Limin.

355
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:13,580
Director Chen.

356
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:14,620
Going out?

357
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:16,780
What do you mean you didn't see him?

358
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:18,740
What kind of a cop are you?

359
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:20,220
We already went to Zhangtou Village,

360
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:21,260
but he wasn't there.

361
00:22:21,420 --> 00:22:23,630
Could he have gone
somewhere else to find a prostitute?

362
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:24,500
Morning, Director Chen.

363
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:25,460
I don't care where he went for that.

364
00:22:25,460 --> 00:22:26,460
What's going on upstairs?

365
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:28,110
Someone's reporting a case
to Director Tong.

366
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:30,140
Go back for now.

367
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:31,980
As soon as there's news,

368
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,460
I'll tell you immediately.

369
00:22:33,700 --> 00:22:34,540
Tong,

370
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:35,510
you have to let me know

371
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:37,220
the moment you find him.

372
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,080
Don't worry,

373
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,060
I'll definitely tell you.

374
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:41,300
I'm sending people
to check again right now.

375
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:42,860
Don't keep playing me.

376
00:22:42,860 --> 00:22:43,970
Go on, just go back.

377
00:22:44,380 --> 00:22:45,220
Don't cry.

378
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,260
Xiaoyun, what's wrong?

379
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:47,740
Hongbing,

380
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:49,740
Yang Baichun is missing.

381
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:51,660
He's missing...

382
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:53,380
Relax.

383
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:55,700
Xiaoyun.

384
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:57,740
What's going on?

385
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:00,620
Last night,

386
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:02,380
Luo Xiaoyun came to report

387
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:04,780
that Yang Baichun went to Zhangtou Village
for a prostitute.

388
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,060
I took some men

389
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:08,900
to Zhangtou Village.

390
00:23:09,740 --> 00:23:10,740
We actually busted

391
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,380
a prostitution ring.

392
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,260
But at the scene,

393
00:23:13,260 --> 00:23:14,540
we didn't find Yang Baichun.

394
00:23:14,540 --> 00:23:15,420
Early this morning,

395
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,460
Luo Xiaoyun came back

396
00:23:17,140 --> 00:23:18,140
saying Yang Baichun

397
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,620
hasn't returned

398
00:23:19,620 --> 00:23:21,380
since he left yesterday.

399
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,460
This isn't normal.

400
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:27,220
What do you mean?

401
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:28,260
Director Tong,

402
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:29,220
I know

403
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:30,060
Yang Baichun.

404
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:32,620
His position as the guesthouse manager

405
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:34,340
is very important to him.

406
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:36,140
No matter what happens,

407
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:38,220
he would never miss work.

408
00:23:39,780 --> 00:23:41,100
Interesting.

409
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:43,820
Huo Kaiming just returned,

410
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:46,420
Huang Liang got burned,

411
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:48,700
and now Yang Baichun

412
00:23:49,540 --> 00:23:50,700
goes missing.

413
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:54,980
Do you think this is a coincidence?

414
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:58,620
I know this can't be rushed.

415
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:00,500
See if you can...

416
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:01,910
Can you help me think of something?

417
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,780
I'll pay whatever it takes,

418
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:04,620
Doctor...

419
00:24:07,500 --> 00:24:08,660
Yes, I am.

420
00:24:09,180 --> 00:24:10,220
Don't hang up yet, Doctor.

421
00:24:23,340 --> 00:24:24,180
What's wrong?

422
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,460
Things aren't going well
with the business?

423
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,300
It's nothing.

424
00:24:30,180 --> 00:24:31,020
Limin,

425
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,980
I want to take Songge out for a trip.

426
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:33,820
Not right now.

427
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:36,780
The two of you cannot leave
the police's sight right now.

428
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:40,100
Songge's physical condition
is getting worse and worse.

429
00:24:40,100 --> 00:24:41,020
I want to take her

430
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:43,460
to Beijing or Shanghai
to see if we can find a kidney donor.

431
00:24:46,980 --> 00:24:48,020
That makes sense.

432
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:49,700
Going out of town

433
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:51,220
is safer than staying here.

434
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:52,620
Yes.

435
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:53,660
That's what I was thinking.

436
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:54,660
Alright.

437
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:56,340
I'll go report to my leaders.

438
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:57,180
Wait for my word.

439
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,900
Hongbing.

440
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:10,100
It's alright.

441
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:11,820
Lie down.

442
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,220
How is the recovery going?

443
00:25:13,980 --> 00:25:14,820
I'm fine, Hongbing.

444
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:15,660
I won't die.

445
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:18,220
I'm telling you, Hongbing.

446
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,780
With Huo Kaiming's ability,

447
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,900
he wants to kill me?

448
00:25:22,820 --> 00:25:23,780
It's just that my health

449
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:24,940
isn't great right now.

450
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:26,020
If this were a couple of years ago,

451
00:25:26,020 --> 00:25:27,740
I would've eliminated him
for the people.

452
00:25:27,740 --> 00:25:28,900
Alright.

453
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,460
Just lie down.

454
00:25:31,100 --> 00:25:32,100
Don't I know you?

455
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:34,460
I want to ask you something.

456
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,700
You're close with Yang Baichun.

457
00:25:36,700 --> 00:25:38,540
Between Yang Baichun and Huo Kaiming,

458
00:25:38,540 --> 00:25:39,620
was there

459
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:40,900
any sort of grudge?

460
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,500
Yang Baichun and Huo Kaiming?

461
00:25:44,860 --> 00:25:46,540
What kind of grudge could they have?

462
00:25:49,260 --> 00:25:50,100
What's up?

463
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,810
Did something happen
to Yang Baichun too?

464
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:53,100
It's not certain yet.

465
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:01,420
Director Tong.

466
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:04,900
What did you say?

467
00:26:06,980 --> 00:26:07,820
He's been found?

468
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:12,940
Baichun,

469
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,100
have some water.

470
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:14,980
Don't be afraid.

471
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,820
What happened?

472
00:26:16,140 --> 00:26:18,100
When the villagers of Liugou found him,

473
00:26:18,100 --> 00:26:19,110
he was already like this.

474
00:26:20,220 --> 00:26:21,060
Baichun.

475
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:22,970
Baichun.

476
00:26:22,970 --> 00:26:23,820
Yang Baichun!

477
00:26:24,100 --> 00:26:25,060
It's me, Chen Hongbing.

478
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,660
Don't you recognize me anymore?

479
00:26:28,020 --> 00:26:28,860
Baichun, you...

480
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:29,700
It hurts.

481
00:26:30,620 --> 00:26:31,740
Come on, help him up.

482
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:34,180
Come on.

483
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:36,620
Get up.

484
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:39,220
Don't be afraid.

485
00:26:39,820 --> 00:26:40,700
Don't move!

486
00:26:40,700 --> 00:26:41,650
Stop it, stop it.

487
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,180
Quiet.

488
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:44,220
What's going on with him?

489
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:46,580
We've asked everything.

490
00:26:46,580 --> 00:26:47,980
He's not making any sense.

491
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,100
And we discovered

492
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:50,900
on his neck right here,

493
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:52,340
there are burn marks from a taser.

494
00:26:52,340 --> 00:26:53,180
A taser?

495
00:26:56,620 --> 00:26:57,460
Calm down.

496
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:58,540
Don't move.

497
00:26:58,540 --> 00:26:59,540
This is coke.

498
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,390
Yes.

499
00:27:00,390 --> 00:27:01,510
He never goes down the mine.

500
00:27:01,620 --> 00:27:02,880
Where did this stuff come from?

501
00:27:03,420 --> 00:27:04,340
It's all over him.

502
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:06,420
He's black all over.

503
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:08,680
It's like he just crawled up
from the bottom of a mine.

504
00:27:10,300 --> 00:27:11,450
- Baichun.
- Hold him down.

505
00:27:11,450 --> 00:27:12,580
- Hold him down.
- Quiet.

506
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:14,140
Don't move.

507
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,170
- Hold him down.
- It's okay.

508
00:27:16,170 --> 00:27:17,420
Quiet.

509
00:27:21,620 --> 00:27:22,740
It's okay, let us just look.

510
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:23,580
Just look.

511
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:24,420
Don't be afraid.

512
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:25,420
Baichun.

513
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:31,420
This is bad.

514
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:33,060
Big guy,

515
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:35,020
take this to the Technical Department
of the municipal PSB.

516
00:27:35,020 --> 00:27:35,910
Have them identify it.

517
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:38,220
Maybe there will be other clues.

518
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,900
Alright, I'll go contact them now.

519
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:43,980
Don't be afraid.

520
00:27:43,980 --> 00:27:45,620
These pants were burned by fire.

521
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:55,020
What is it?

522
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:56,580
Potassium permanganate.

523
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:57,620
Potassium permanganate?

524
00:27:58,780 --> 00:27:59,780
It's Huo Kaiming again.

525
00:28:00,820 --> 00:28:01,660
The map!

526
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,740
Director Tong,

527
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:07,660
coke production

528
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:08,980
requires 24-hour

529
00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:09,980
on-site staffing.

530
00:28:09,980 --> 00:28:10,820
Correct.

531
00:28:10,820 --> 00:28:11,720
If it were Huo Kaiming,

532
00:28:11,730 --> 00:28:13,300
and he really wanted
to burn him to death,

533
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,700
he would choose

534
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,820
a coking plant
that has already been shut down.

535
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:17,660
Right now,

536
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:18,740
we need to find

537
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:19,980
this shut-down plant.

538
00:28:19,980 --> 00:28:21,260
There's one in Liugou Village.

539
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:24,020
Yang Baichun was found near there.

540
00:28:24,020 --> 00:28:26,110
Let's start the investigation
from that coking plant.

541
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:27,780
Director Tong,

542
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,700
all of these matters now

543
00:28:29,700 --> 00:28:30,820
involve Huo Kaiming.

544
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:32,700
Shouldn't we

545
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:34,100
inform the municipal PSB?

546
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:35,900
I'll contact them immediately.

547
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:55,740
Director Chen.

548
00:29:02,260 --> 00:29:03,100
Limin.

549
00:29:03,300 --> 00:29:04,140
Master.

550
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:05,380
Did you find anything?

551
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:07,710
The car is Yang Baichun's.

552
00:29:07,780 --> 00:29:08,620
But that day,

553
00:29:08,620 --> 00:29:09,460
it rained.

554
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:10,920
There isn't even
a single footprint on the ground.

555
00:29:28,420 --> 00:29:29,260
What's wrong, Master?

556
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,980
Are there any other findings?

557
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:34,100
By the way, Master,

558
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:35,900
Huang Liang told me

559
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:37,420
that when Huo Kaiming attacked him,

560
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,260
he was driving
this kind of farm tricycle.

561
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:40,980
So I was thinking,

562
00:29:41,620 --> 00:29:43,510
if this vehicle
really belongs to Huo Kaiming,

563
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:45,940
it means Huo Kaiming wanted
to kill Yang Baichun.

564
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:47,900
It's probably not that simple.

565
00:29:48,580 --> 00:29:49,940
Well, why didn't Yang Baichun die?

566
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:52,700
And why did Huo Kaiming
want to kill him?

567
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,340
What were

568
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:57,180
they doing out in such a remote place?

569
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:01,640
Kang Limin, come and look at this.

570
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:08,180
Look.

571
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,300
What's this?

572
00:30:15,860 --> 00:30:17,020
Blood must have flowed here,

573
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:18,180
but after being washed by the rain,

574
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:19,210
it's hard to see clearly.

575
00:30:20,780 --> 00:30:21,820
Such a large area?

576
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:25,060
Regardless of whose blood it is,

577
00:30:25,060 --> 00:30:26,620
this person likely won't survive.

578
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,300
Okay.

579
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:40,300
Alright.

580
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:41,980
Understood.

581
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:49,260
Why are you looking at me?

582
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:50,900
Say it straight.

583
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:56,060
The data from Yang Baichun's phone

584
00:30:56,060 --> 00:30:56,980
has been recovered.

585
00:30:57,660 --> 00:30:58,580
The last shutdown time

586
00:30:58,580 --> 00:30:59,980
was at 8:30 PM on the 27th.

587
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,540
8:30 PM.

588
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:04,940
8:30 PM

589
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:06,260
should be

590
00:31:06,940 --> 00:31:08,020
the time of the incident.

591
00:31:11,580 --> 00:31:12,420
Master,

592
00:31:13,180 --> 00:31:14,060
Yang Baichun's

593
00:31:14,060 --> 00:31:15,580
last call record

594
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:16,620
was with Hui.

595
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:22,900
What?

596
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:25,860
It was with Hui.

597
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,980
There's one more thing.

598
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,540
Yesterday, Hui told me

599
00:31:30,540 --> 00:31:32,180
he wanted to take Songge on a long trip.

600
00:31:41,540 --> 00:31:42,380
Limin,

601
00:31:44,580 --> 00:31:46,060
however you need to investigate,

602
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:47,900
just do it.

603
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:50,780
I will recuse myself.

604
00:31:51,260 --> 00:31:52,100
Master.

605
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,380
Xiaoyun,

606
00:32:08,380 --> 00:32:09,220
you

607
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:10,220
must stay strong.

608
00:32:10,850 --> 00:32:12,380
Since things have already come to this,

609
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:13,260
don't dwell on it.

610
00:32:14,380 --> 00:32:15,500
Don't cry.

611
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:16,860
If you need any help,

612
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:18,020
you must call me.

613
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:20,620
Move on.

614
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:21,460
Alright.

615
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:25,140
How could Xiaoyun

616
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:26,420
be so unlucky?

617
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:28,940
She ended up with Yang Baichun

618
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:30,180
and suffered for a lifetime.

619
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:32,180
Now that her daughter
has finally made it to the university,

620
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:33,300
Yang Baichun has gone crazy.

621
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:36,740
You know,

622
00:32:39,140 --> 00:32:40,540
before Yang Baichun's accident,

623
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,580
the very last call

624
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:45,900
was from Hui to him.

625
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:50,620
Hui?

626
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:55,540
Do you know what this implies?
